IF EXISTS ( SELECT * FROM sys.external_tables WHERE object_id = OBJECT_ID('dbo.D_STWaybillInServiceReasons') )
    DROP EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.D_STWaybillInServiceReasons
GO

CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.D_STWaybillInServiceReasons (
    [lms_inservicereason_id] bigint,
    [lms_inservicereason_description] nvarchar(4000),
    [lms_inservicereason_group] nvarchar(4000),


	)
	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'Structured Data/OPS/stwaybillinservicereasons.parquet',
	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseParquetFormat]
	)
GO


SELECT TOP 100 * FROM dbo.D_STWaybillInServiceReasons 
GO
